CFB Venue Information

cfb_venues.Rd

Pulls all college football venues and data on capacity, grass, city/state, location, elevation, dome, timezone and construction year

cfb_venues()

Source

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/venues

Value

A data frame with 335 rows and 13 variables:

venue_id

integer.

name

character.

capacity

integer.

grass

logical.

city

character.

state

character.

zip

character.

country_code

character.

location

list.

elevation

character.

year_constructed

integer.

dome

logical.

timezone

character.
